<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="threat-n">threat <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /θret/    美 /θret/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>威胁；恐吓：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The <strong>threat of</strong> war has depressed business activity.
由于战争的威胁，商业活动变得不景气了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>构成威胁的人 / 事物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Pollution <strong>poses a threat to</strong> the continued existence of this species. 
污染对这一物种的生存造成威胁。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>凶兆：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There was a <strong>threat of</strong> typhoon. 
有刮台风的征兆。</p></div></div>